Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with optimal control problems and stability analysis, which are topics related to systems and control. 
- cs.OH (Other Computer Science): The paper does not fit neatly into any specific sub-category, so it could be classified as "other". 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Approximate Dynamic Programming is a type of reinforcement learning, which falls under the umbrella of machine learning. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper involves numerical analysis of the convergence and stability of a numerical method for solving optimal control problems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with a type of AI algorithm (ADP) and its performance with approximation errors.
